flowRoot.flowPara: openSUSE is a free Linux-based operating system for your PC. You can surf the web, manage your e-mails and photos, do office work, play videos or music
An openSUSE DVD includes everything you need to get your desktop, laptop, or server up and running with Linux in no time!
